gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Suns 126, Jazz 104
gameRecap.excerpt: The Suns defeated the Jazz, 126-104. Kevin Durant recorded 26 points (8-11 FG), 4 rebounds and 7 assists for the Suns, while Eric Gordon added 21 points and 4 assists in the victory. Lauri Markkanen tallied 19 points (7-13 FG) and 3 rebounds for the Jazz in the losing effort. The Suns improve to 2-1 on the season, while the Jazz fall to 1-2.
